{"tid":25421,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"指拒答議員提問違《基本法》　覆核王入稟控曾俊華、袁國強","createTime":"2016-12-06T06:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-06T07:01:11.000Z","uid":25556,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5d24b2703782b64605ec8de12ec729698d93dd75","tid":25421,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:12:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/kowk-08_fuNVN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fkowk-08_fuNVN_1200x0.png&h=45a32ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n財政司司長曾俊華昨日出席立法會會議時，根據律政司的意見拒絕回答被政府入稟司法覆核的四名議員之提問。有「長洲覆核王」之稱的郭卓堅，今日便入稟高院申請司法覆核，控告曾俊華以及律政司司長袁國強。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅引用《基本法》64條認為，政府需要答覆立法會議員的質詢，但曾俊華昨日在立法會，卻表示不會回答四名議員的提問。他要求法庭頒令，指律政司向政府提供有關法律意見，屬錯誤、非法及違反《基本法》，並要求法庭頒令聲明，要政府官員按照《基本法》辦事。<br />\n<br />\n他親手撰寫入稟狀到法院，但就在庭外坦言沒有信心今次司法覆核申請會獲批。他又指今次入稟是要令全世界知道「袁國強連小學都未畢業」，批評對方不懂法律。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華昨日在立法會財經事務委員會會議上，主動表示因有關法律程序進行中，不會回應4名議員劉小麗、梁國雄、羅冠聰、姚松炎提問。但政務司司長林鄭月娥下午改口，表示官員會答所有議員提問。特首梁振英今日出席行政會議前回應事件，稱事先不知曾俊華不回應四名議員的提問。"},{"pid":"e7427dbe1379e22f602db1aa8325016163377576","tid":25421,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:13:00.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"652d0c8106c3f32059e68bf1ded1ddbcbd5cc101","tid":25421,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93202c6d15e0544a8069fb0fa5d17b69fba96e94","tid":25421,"uid":5489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:18:14.000Z","msg":"識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本應該咁做"},{"pid":"a9eeaadf6b0ae59de32545485f02091941d95382","tid":25421,"uid":49609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b17471e43bc5c3405405e76bb595a6cddffc28","tid":25421,"uid":54622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b29d51a85568291e2daa00ed6b5bdd3468363c","tid":25421,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:20:49.000Z","msg":"佢禁多錢既"},{"pid":"701a2bf16e0946ad54066f01087beb77d5ae17fc","tid":25421,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:24:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢禁多錢既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n法援"},{"pid":"b97946cbcb1e33dc21fa800eaf382b0acd6eea33","tid":25421,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:52:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7909063296126c0948faeb0e1fbca40accc67808","tid":25421,"uid":34037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:53:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5186c1ab5072a7fab29e3952c10b7b7e176d40b1","tid":25421,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38d6b4b7a1e6b14b14487be98be80e44836c954c","tid":25421,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢禁多錢既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n法援</blockquote><br />\n呢d先係善用社會資源<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89bca705eb045ac605af0435f5cda8ae613e0011","tid":25421,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016